## Contributing

1. Branch from `main`: `git checkout -b feature/your-feature-name`
2. Never commit `.env`, service account JSON, or any credentials
3. Run `pip freeze > requirements.txt` after adding dependencies
4. Test the health endpoint and at least one extraction before opening a PR
5. All PRs require review from a second engineer before merging to `main`

